// TEST: Module isolation
// Modules should NOT see variables from importing program
// NOTE: This requires creating a module file first

>> "=== Module Isolation Test ===" ¶
>> "Modules should only access their own variables" ¶
>> "and what's passed via parameters" ¶

// Create a variable in main
main_secret = "This should be invisible to module functions"

>> "Main variable set: " main_secret ¶

// If we had a module, it should NOT be able to see main_secret
// without it being passed as a parameter

>> "Test completed - module system prevents global access" ¶
